Whether football comes home or not this Sunday, nothing can take away the sheer joy the England team has brought to the country during the Euro 2020 tournament. Win or lose, we have a national team that feels truly 21st century and who have managed to provide a sense of unity, pride and hope in a country still in the grips of the pandemic. Here are 15 moments that have made our collective hearts swell... Watch England take on Italy in the Euro 2020 Final on BBC One and ITV, Sunday at 8pm.